BCEL:
http://jakarta.apache.org/bcel/

cd ~/java/
wget http://jakarta.apache.org/builds/jakarta-bcel/release/v5.1/bcel-5.1.tar.gz
tar zxf bcel-5.1.tar.gz

Now add ~/java/bcel-5.1/bcel-5.1.jar to my CLASSPATH
